From: Pratyush Yadav <p.yadav@ti.com>

Allow flashes to specify a hook to enable octal DTR mode. Use this hook
whenever possible to get optimal transfer speeds.

Signed-off-by: Pratyush Yadav <p.yadav@ti.com>
